        public MacLearningSpec.Builder setLimit(java.lang.Long limit)
        This property specifies the limit on the maximum number of MAC addresses that can be learned on a port. It is consumed by vswitch kernel module on the hypervisor while learning MACs per port for VMs that are local to the host. format: int32
        Parameters:
